                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#faq2" class="collapsed question">
                            What is Tana return policy? <i style="margin-top: 7px;" class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down icon-show"></i><i style="margin-top: 7px;" class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right icon-close"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div id="faq2" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
