                                All Tana purchases have an extended 60-day return policy (some exceptions apply).<br />

                                All purchases made on Tana.com, in any of the Tana apps, or at a Tana store have a 60-day return period. Go ahead and test out your Tana or Converse purchase to make sure it works for you.<br />

                                You can return items (some exceptions apply) for any reason within those 60 days. That includes custom Tana By You sneakers. Even after 60 days, you can still return items if they’re unworn and unwashed. And remember, returns are always free for Tana Members.<br />

                                So go ahead, shop with confidence, and enjoy your 60-day trial.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#faq3" class="collapsed question">
                            Do Tana shoes have a warranty? <i style="margin-top: 7px;" class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down icon-show"></i><i style="margin-top: 7px;" class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right icon-close"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div id="faq3" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
