                        </div>
                        <div id="faq4" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
                            <p>
                                <b>Tana Membership</b> gives you access to inspiration, community, and exclusive Tana products. It’s the best way to access everything Nike and it’s free, fast, and easy to join. You can join online or when you download any of the Tana apps. And you’ll enjoy immediate benefits:<br />

                                <b>Free shipping (and returns).</b> Just sign in when you shop and you’ll automatically get free standard shipping and free shipping for returns.<br />
                                <b>Member Shop.</b> A unique collection of Tana shoes and gear that is only available to Tana Members.<br />
                                <b>Deals.</b> Special offers and promos to thank our Members and to celebrate big moments, like birthdays.<br />

                            </p>
                        </div>
