                                You can't make changes, but you can cancel an order within 30 minutes of placing it.<br />

                                To cancel an order, first go to your orders page. If you’re not signed in, you’ll need to enter your order number from your order confirmation email, along with your email address. Next, open the order you want to cancel, then tap or click the “Cancel” button and follow the prompts.<br />

